16:05:43','2015-03-24 20:05:43','',88,'http://adomattic.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/contextual-ads.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(106,1,'2015-03-24 16:05:51','2015-03-24 20:05:51','Contextual advertisements take place using specific keywords from the websites or from the search terms used by consumers. The websites that are targeted to some specific area contain keywords which are used by contextual advertisement scripts to produce and display relevant advertisements to the visitors. Such as website dedicated to food recopies will contain words relevant to foods hence script will fetch the advertisements of best food restaurants or newly written books on continental foods. Contextual advertisements can be displayed as ads on website with other web content or as pop-ups. Search engines display contextual advertisements by showing them in search results to the searcher.\r\n\r\n<b>Latest trends in contextual advertisement</b>\r\n\r\n<b>            </b>Advanced trends, enhanced scripts and faster algorithms are used to display relevant advertisements on a webpage. Here we are mentioning some latest trends and facts about contextual advertisement.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Developers and advertisers are introducing new trends to present customized information and message to their audience. Several ways are devised to fetch more information about the consumers.</li>\r\n	<li>Showing relevant advertisements on web-pages is the core motive of contextual advertisement. Programmers are using latest technologies called Mediabot and Googlebot to fetch related advertisements only.</li>\r\n	<li>Gaming is also used as a mean to advertise but in the beginning experience did not produce positive results. Companies embedded advertisements at the time game was loading but players showed great annoyance. Advertisers are now searching for better ways. Many games are now inserting advertisements at different scenes of games without effecting player’s game experience.</li>\r\n	<li>Video-on-video or text on video at the time of loading is also applied. ScanScout and Adsense is a latest technology that scans the content of video and offer only relevant advertisements. Adribe is a technique that shows text advertisements on videos.</li>\r\n	<li>Publishers and advertisers now prefer collaborative working to earn more profit. Both Google and Yahoo have introduced their own ways of pricing at advertisements. Google’s smart pricing scheme allows setting prices dynamically while yahoo lets to set one price for each company rather than setting dynamic costs for products.</li>\r\n	<li>The trend that will be more common in near future is billboard contextual advertising. This advertising comprises using cameras with billboards and recording the expressions, time duration person spent on reading advertisements, and their responses. Advertisers can use this direct information for further functions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b> Controversies</b>\r\n\r\nContextual advertisements called to controversies when unfair means were used to display them on sites without paying them. Third party software is installed on visitor’s computer. This software interacts with the browser and converts keywords on the websites into hyperlinks to the advertisements without paying the website. This technique is known as Third part hyperlinking. There are many such techniques used to illegally advertise on the websites without their permission.\r\n\r\nDifferent formats of Contextual advertisement not just compute users preferences but their behaviors as well. Developers and advertisers are working to enhance the ways of displaying advertisements to the relevant users. Contextual advertisement is now becoming one of the major sources of earning for websites.\r\n\r\nPhoto Credit: https://www.flickr.com/photos/proimos/','What Is Contextual Advertisement?','','inherit','open','open','','88-revision-v1','','','2015-03-24 16:05:51','2015-03-24 20:05:51','',88,'http://adomattic.com/88-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(107,1,'2015-03-24 17:18:08','2015-03-24 21:18:08','','display_advertising','','inherit','open','open','','confectionary','','','2015-03-24 17:18:45','2015-03-24 21:18:45','',86,'http://adomattic.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/confectionary.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(108,1,'2015-03-24 17:18:52','2015-03-24 21:18:52','Display advertising is the advertisement taking place on World Wide Web. It can have a range of formats that are images, logos, videos, audios or text. The reason of display advertising is to advertise your product or service to millions of folks joining Internet daily. The advent of internet since 90’s has completely changed the way of communicating information to people. It deeply affected the way of advertisements and the way people are informed. Prices of computers got decreased while their uses moved upward. People created multiple channels on internet to reach global market and to obtain millions of online visitors daily.\r\n\r\n<strong>Top display advertising trends</strong>\r\n\r\nDigital world is evolving rapidly than ever before. Social media algorithms, SEO trends, website programming and search codes are changed almost every day. Latest Web programming and designing languages are getting modified daily to allow rich display advertising ranging from videos to gaming. Advertisers and publishers need to be abreast of all the latest trends. Here we have given some top display advertising trends of 2014 and 2015.\r\n\r\n<strong>Context and content</strong>\r\n\r\nContext and quality content hold immense importance to for the engagement of customer. When advertisement gets shifted from to online and reduced view-ability becomes an issue as media contents such as videos are less controllable then the risk of losing customer’s interest goes higher.\r\n\r\nNew ad packages are being created which combine editorial and ad creative snippets then organize these to ad networks and marketplaces. Latest technologies and online platforms are allowing ads to be remotely published up to exact parts of a publisher’s page indexed according to their content. These trends are creating ad syndication models we could only vision about in the past.\r\n\r\n<strong>More programmatic advertising</strong>\r\n\r\nPlacing ads online automatically use Artificial intelligence and real-time bidding to automate the decision-making process of online purchases, fall in the category of programmatic advertising. More than forty percent of display advertisements including rich media such as videos, audios and images are published to the consumers using automated scripts. Automated E-mails and mobile texts are sent to customers about the recent updates. This trend got great deal of fame and application in 2014.\r\n\r\n<strong>Data is key driver to your display advertisement</strong>\r\n\r\nData is a key driver of your advertisement. It’s not an association of brand with prospects but the association of details with buyers. The provided data and content must be relevant to advertisement. You need to focus more on personalization, co-branding and cross promoting in your display advertising processes.\r\n\r\n<strong>Display advertising formats</strong>\r\n\r\nOne of the most essential aspects of display advertising is its format. Formats put psychological effects over your customers and attract them. Two major types of formats are banner advertising and sponsored content. Other formats are videos, overlays, sponsorship, text and rich media ads.\r\n\r\nDisplay advertisements appear next to your content on your webpage, hence are not annoying. They are better than spam E-mails and pop-ups that block webpage for few seconds. it has been proved as the fastest and reliable way of communicating advertisement. Programmatic advertisements can boost-up the success of your business.\r\n\r\n<strong>      </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Display Advertising Trends','','inherit','open','open','','86-autosave-v1','','','2015-03-24 17:18:52','