 more common in near future is billboard contextual advertising. This advertising comprises using cameras with billboards and recording the expressions, time duration person spent on reading advertisements, and their responses. Advertisers can use this direct information for further functions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b> Controversies</b>\r\n\r\nContextual advertisements called to controversies when unfair means were used to display them on sites without paying them. Third party software is installed on visitor’s computer. This software interacts with the browser and converts keywords on the websites into hyperlinks to the advertisements without paying the website. This technique is known as Third part hyperlinking. There are many such techniques used to illegally advertise on the websites without their permission.\r\n\r\nDifferent formats of Contextual advertisement not just compute users preferences but their behaviors as well. Developers and advertisers are working to enhance the ways of displaying advertisements to the relevant users. Contextual advertisement is now becoming one of the major sources of earning for websites.\r\n\r\nPhoto Credit: https://www.flickr.com/photos/proimos/','What Is Contextual Advertisement?','','inherit','open','open','','88-autosave-v1','','','2015-03-26 13:02:35','2015-03-26 17:02:35','',88,'http://adomattic.com/88-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(145,1,'2015-03-27 14:11:54','2015-03-27 18:11:54','Adomattic is turning technology innovations into  business results.\r\n\r\nWe evaluate new emerging technologies and identify marketing opportunities for large enterprises to apply them in their product/project cycles to break new grounds and steer ahead of competition.\r\n\r\nOur current toolbox for 2015 is\r\n\r\n1) Graph Technologies - Neo4j\r\n2) Artificial Intelligence Warehousing\r\n3) Scalable Web Crawlers - Apache Nutch\r\n4) Key Value Data Stores - Accumulo\r\n5) Data Visualization using Python and R\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Labs',