strong>Famous mobile advertising companies</strong>\r\n\r\nMultinational companies of Google and Microsoft are also taking part in this race by introducing their own ways of mobile advertisements. Google provides mobile targeting in its fast growing advertising program <strong>Google Adwords </strong>and has also provided well known mobile advertising program names<strong> Google Admob Ads,</strong> while Microsoft is also providing techniques to build powerful mobile ads with the options to target specific locations, device type, and platforms used that are iOS, Android and windows phone. Mobile phone versions of Microsoft products like Skype, Bing and MSN are used to display relevant ads. While using Skype you can see ads on its home page. Recent study has revealed that around 70% people use mobile version of apps.\r\n\r\nFew top mobile advertising companies are Google Admob Ads, Millennial Media, Apple’s iAd, Flurry, InMobi, ChartBoost, HasOffers and Amobee. You can use services of these mobile advertising companies to publish your ad. All have their own policies and bidding methods.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://www.adweek.com/socialtimes/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/07/Screen-Shot-2012-07-18-at-9.28.24-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"353\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Tips </strong>\r\n\r\nHere we are presenting few mobile advertising tips you should follow to boost your mobile advertisment.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Increase your click-through rates by avoiding additional clicks and engaging customers more in sign-up newsletters and by providing eye catching mobile ads.</li>\r\n	<li>Make any game or useful mobile app that people will use so you will advertise your business as well.</li>\r\n	<li>Make your ad to be presented at the right time when they are needed. For instance if someone in your area is searching on Google (through mobile) about nearby hotels than your ad must be displayed so consumers will quickly click over your ad.</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize your ad according to time, location and device.</li>\r\n	<li>Offer robust call to action offers such as buy one get one free or buy it now and save your 40%.</li>\r\n	<li>Customize your ads to be shareable on social networking websites such as Facebook, Twitter, Orcut and LinkedIn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTake in consideration how mobile advertising and mobile marketing can fit in with your marketing program and how it can strengthen your association with your consumers. Once you measure all analytics and understand how you need to reach your customers on mobiles then you can start creating compelling and relevant messages but with great care.','Mobile Advertising-Stay around your customer','','inherit','open','open','','174-revision-v1','','','2015-03-31 12:08:24','2015-03-31 16:08:24','',174,'http://adomattic.com/174-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(194,1,'2015-03-31 12:17:32','2015-03-31 16:17:32','','mobile advertising','','inherit','open','open','','mobile-advertising-2','','','2015-03-31 12:17:32','2015-03-31 16:17:32','',174,'http://adomattic.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/mobile-advertising1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(195,1,'2015-03-31 12:27:51','2015-03-31 16:27:51','','mobile advertising','','inherit','open','open','','mobile-advertising','','','2015-03-31 12:27:51','2015-03-31 16:27:51','',174,'http://adomattic.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/mobile-advertising.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(198,2,'2015-04-08 19:22:53','2015-04-08 23:22:53','Artificial intelligence is a field of science that studies and describes intelligent behavior in computational devices and applications. Intelligent behavior shows power of taking decisions, making logic, learning and solving problems. AI is widely used in different fields. Artificial intelligence in marketing is used for the reason to achieve automation, accurate outputs, time and effort efficiency, decision making and to predict future market statistics. Currently largest companies such as Facebook, Google, Twitter and Amazon are using AI techniques to collect more data about their consumers and to stay in stronger connection with them. AI has provided revolutionary ways for companies to collect customer information, its assessment and making decisions based on those evaluations.\r\n\r\n<strong>Emergence of personal intelligent assistant</strong>\r\n\r\nPersonal intelligent assistant (also called virtual assistant) AI based software agents that can carry out different tasks based on user inputs, their locations and other criteria. Important tasks they can do are;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Check weather to guide which direction you should take</li>\r\n	<li>Displays and guides about products based on your search criteria and price range</li>\r\n	<li>Finds suitable restaurants, shows or shopping malls in town</li>\r\n	<li>Scheduling managements</li>\r\n	<li>Personal health management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere are also a lot more tasks it can perform. For marketers it has almost cut 60% cost of human employees as they only need to buy, run and use the software which doesn\'t ask for any salary or extra facilities of course.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Role of AI in trust-able advertising</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>            </strong> Artificial intelligence based advertising assistant software communicate with consumers, suggest them best products, guide them about different things similarly as a sales-person does in any shop. Automatic processes work to notify customers about discounts, latest offers, and new products. Buyer’s data is more organized and secure which makes them trust AI-powered software. These apps are used to educate customers rather than making them feels invasive like outdated advertisement formats. Users are always more interested in optimizing their tasks, this will make them trust AI-powered apps and they will share information with it. Advertisers and businesses can further utilize this data to anticipate future user behaviors and preferences.\r\n\r\n<strong>How it helps in decision making?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>            </strong>Marketing field is 80% dependent on making good decision at appropriate times. Marketers must have deep insights and great judgment powers.  Customers needs are growing so are their preferences, this has turned traditional ways of making decisions hard to control anymore. AI provides decision support systems that combine business strategies and business goals to produce best decisions. These techniques are highly extending customer support, decision making, optimizing data, market forecasting, decreasing data overload and providing new trends of team communication methods.\r\n\r\n<strong>Use of AI to evaluate online social networks</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>            </strong>Social websites are used by companies and business groups to spread their network socially. AI facilitates us with Agent-based social simulation software and techniques used to collect and assess social information of business networks. This data and assessments can help marketers to understand marketplace, segments and assists in gaining large audience.\r\n\r\n<strong>            </strong>For many companies AI techniques are quite new and challenging but their applications are a lot more beneficial than traditional marketing and advertising techniques.<img src=\"https://conductricsblog.files.wordpress.com/2012/08/agent_general.png\" alt=\"Artificial Intelligence in marketing\" />\r\n\r\n<i>image by conductrics at their website {link to <a href=\"http://blog.conductrics.com/\" title=\"conductrics\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.conductrics.com/</a>} </i>','Artificial intelligence in marketing','','publish','open','open','','artificial-intelligence-marketing','','','2015-04-24 06:42:23','2015-04-24 10:42:23','',0,'http://adomattic.com/?p=198',0,'post','',1),(199,2,'2015-04-01 10:24:20','2015-04-01 14:24:20','Artificial intelligence is a field 