, natural search, E-mail ad or video and audio ad.</li>\r\n	<li>Allows cross platform tracking.</li>\r\n	<li>Image advertisements (banners can be run on Google\'s AdSense Network) could be merged to DART for Publishers</li>\r\n</ul>','How Google DoubleClick helps in marketing?','','inherit','open','open','','213-revision-v1','','','2015-04-03 11:55:26','2015-04-03 15:55:26','',213,'http://adomattic.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(222,2,'2015-04-15 11:46:53','2015-04-15 15:46:53','<h3>What is Paid search?</h3>\r\nPaid search is online advertising term used for procedure where results, analysis, targeting and traffic are dictated by payments from advertisers. Many link the word “paid search” with search engine marketing (SEM), pay-per-click, SEO, search engine advertising and cost per impression.  Paid search is also related to some definite forms of business relationship where advertisers have to pay search engines or other websites and web hosts when their ads are clicked or less often, when they are displayed, that gives the host entity the reason to display ads in search engine results.\r\n\r\n <img src=\"http://www.twiobrand.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Twio_PaidSearch_Infographic1.png\" alt=\"paid search\" />\r\n\r\n<i>image by Twino Brand at their website {link to <a href=\"http://www.twiobrand.com/paid-search/\" title=\" Twino Brand\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twiobrand.com/paid-search/</a>} </i>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThose advertisers who pay more for their ads are more likely to have their ads displayed in search results. For instance if you type “flowers shop” than ads paying more and having better SEO optimization will win top positions on the search page.\r\n<h3>Why Paid search Marketing?</h3>\r\n<strong>            </strong>The most important thing for advertiser is to make ad appear on one of the top five positions of the SERPs (Search Engine Rank Position). This amplifies the possibility of getting clicks from visitors. Remember if you have good investment than PPC (pay per click) is the easiest and fastest method to get your ad on top. If you can work well with the such platforms than it’s just going to take few hours to set display ads such as banners, audio, textual content or any other optimized content. It will emerge in no time in sponsored search results.\r\n\r\nTracking is a lot simpler and easier through SEM now. Advertisers no longer need to take a take risks on ads they have paid for in advance in other media or websites; with ambiguous ways to measure how thriving they are .By using search engine paid ad-servicing each ad, SEO keyword and dime used up can be tracked, resulting in more exact ROI (return to investment). That makes it much easier for you to test advertising campaigns.\r\n\r\nBesides all this, technologies used in SEM enables you to target ads according to locations, timings, languages and other conditions. You can also advertise on Network display and other search engine related sites. These features make paid search an important part of marketing strategies.\r\n<h3>Steps for beginners</h3>\r\nIf you are a newbie and want to know some tips on how you can use paid search marketing strategies to boost your business then you must read following points;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Understand how PPC works and what bidding methods you can use for it.</li>\r\n	<li>Understand conversions and have defined goals of conversions to select proper keywords, and create display ads.</li>\r\n	<li>Chose your PPC platform. It’s better to test different platforms and select which are most appropriate.</li>\r\n	<li>Search related keywords and add into your ad</li>\r\n	<li>Determine your PPC budget and move accordingly</li>\r\n	<li>Design catchy ads</li>\r\n	<li>Make certain your landing pages are relevant and attractive</li>\r\n	<li>Test and optimize ads</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThese tips will make you step into SEM initially. Your product and services must be according to requirement