enges. A recent study by <strong>SalesForce Marketing Cloud </strong>has shown around 84% of global marketers is planning to switch and spend on digital marketing in year 2015. 42% are B2C marketers and 38% are B2B marketers in the survey. Of course there are number of digital advertising channels but most of marketers are planning to spend more on the following top areas;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>More than 70% marketers are thinking to spend social media advertising and marketing.</li>\r\n	<li>Around 67% people are planning to spend on social media engagement.</li>\r\n	<li>67% marketers voted for mobile apps that track customer’s.</li>\r\n	<li>66% marketers preferred using mobile apps to reach their customers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe report showed they are having new digital marketing challenges. Marketers stated that they are trying to create more by spending less and trying to grab their consumers. There are now more means of targeting specific users based on languages, areas, ages, and timing than ever before. All along with confronts digital marketing has fetched so many positive prospects and ease for marketers especially to win real objectives of company.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://i.marketingprofs.com/assets/images/daily-data-point/priorities-LG-salesforce-270115.jpg\" alt=\"digital marketing challenges \" />\r\n\r\n<i>image by marketingprofs at their website {link to <a href=\"http://www.marketingprofs.com/\" title=\"marketingprofs\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.marketingprofs.com/</a>} </i>\r\n\r\nHere are given some major potential crisis in digital marketing;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Meeting prospects of always connect user</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis has emerged as the biggest issue in digital marketing. You can never get attention or can retain it for longer if you are failed in providing what you user is expecting from you. In survey more than 15% marketers highlighted this problem as the very first and main issue. To resolve this issue you must follow latest trends and preferences of your customers. You can conduct any research any questioner to ask your target audience about what they expect from you. You can also ask for their suggestions about what means and channels do they prefer for getting their expected requirements.  <strong> </strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Executing reliable digital campaign that drive digital marketing</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAround 14% people reported it as the second biggest challenge. They said that users will only be attracted to your ads and services if they find them reliable, trustworthy and secure. Digital campaigns must be designed the way that they must provide proves of their authentication to visitors. You can get some verified digital certificates or can use digital signatures to prove your genuineness.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Rapid enhancements in user engaging channels</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn past few years large number of digital ways has been introduced to communicate with the consumer. Now the major target is controlling your ads on all these means appropriately and in organized manner. Marketers must handle these ways professionally, must contribute to informative content and should offer easier ways of communication to the user.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Personalizing customers</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPersonalization raised as one of the serious challenges. Every person has catched different mind than others. Its requirements, preferences and expectations might be different from others. In this case marketers need to be more careful and should personalize their customers.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Pacing with latest trends </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDigital marketing trends are revolving not in weeks but in days. Literacy level about technology is not much higher among common people and marketers. Hence, pacing marketing with latest trends can an issue for them. For resolving it they can get help of virtual assistants, professional, can hire technical people having kno