rtisements. Television utilizes audios, videos and textual content for advertising your business campaigns.\r\n\r\n<img class=\" alignright\" src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7666/17099131926_3224de7a11_b.jpg\" alt=\" Impact of television on marketing \" width=\"377\" height=\"256\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Positive impacts of television on marketing;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Reach global market</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTelevision ads are more general than being specific where marketers can target vast number of audience regardless of any specification. You can use different methods of communicating your information to the consumers using audios, attractive pictures, textual content or informative videos. Especially those channels which are popular among people can be used as best sources for advertising your product or services.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Targeted audience</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith TV targeting, specific segment or customers are bit difficult but you can do it with different provided program. You can target your customers by only broadcasting your product promotion program in specific areas, at specific timing or in any particular language. You can also advertise in between cartoon if your product is any toy, chocolate or any other thing related to kids interest.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Multi sensory appeal</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTV enables marketers to advertise in different formats to grab the customer such as slides, videos, audio ads or other forms of content. But all this needs to be programmed and designed by production experts. This can be considered as one of the most appealing advantage for marketers.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Persuade your customers</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen your ad is broadcasted and customers see it, they never place orders at first view. They might see the ad multiples time which will influence and persuade them to try your product.\r\n<h2>Negative impact of television on marketing;</h2>\r\nJust like every other thing TV ads also have some dark corners. Few are;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>TV ads cost pretty much because channels do only charge for advertising, but they also cash their popularity. Cost also depends on ad duration, when are you broadcasting it and which areas are you broadcasting it in.</li>\r\n	<li>You must pay product experts and other team experts too to prepare your ad.</li>\r\n	<li>If you need to change anything you will have to reshoot the complete ad which will cost double.</li>\r\n	<li>Showing it once or twice to customers is not enough. The ad must be displayed at least 6 or 7 times to the consumer to grab its attention.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTV marketing is suitable for every type of business of any range and size. It can catch the attention of customers for them from anywhere.','Impact of television on marketing','','publish','open','open','','impact-television-marketing','','','2015-04-24 06:07:55','2015-04-24 10:07:55','',0,'http://adomattic.com/?p=246',0,'post','',0),(247,2,'2015-04-09 09:57:45','2015-04-09 13:57:45','Television has been leaving its impacts on advertising since long ago. With encroachments in technology and user demands, number of channels is also increased. Today’s purchaser is multichannel bargain hunter. They crosscheck the information they get from one source with that fetched from any other source. This enables them to be more confident regarding their purchase decisions before they invest their money.\r\n\r\nThis multichannel trend has made TV advertising relative more difficult. Advertisers are studying large granular data for checking where they can more suitably spend their money. They want to use up their wealth on spot which can have stronger and positive force on their businesses. There is still great research needed about how to measure the impacts of television on conversion rates effectively and which channels are affecting it more.\r\n\r\nTV ads have got great reach everywhere. The source is considered mor