/ul>\r\nTelevision ads are more general than being specific where marketers can target vast number of audience regardless of any specification. You can use different methods for communicating your information to the consumers using audios, attractive pictures, textual content or informative videos. Especially those channels which are popular among people can be used as best sources for advertising your product or services.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Targeted audience</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith TV targeting specific segment or customers is bit difficult but you can do it with different provided program. You can target your customers by only broadcasting your product promotion program in specific areas, at specific timing or in any particular language. You can also advertise in between cartoon if your product is any toy, chocolate or any other thing related to kids interest.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Multi sensory appeal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTV enables marketers to advertise in different formats to grab the customer such as slides, videos, audio ads or other forms of content. But all this needs to be programmed and designed by production experts. This can be considered as one of the most appealing advantage for marketers.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Persuade your customers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen your ad is broadcasted and customers see it, they never place orders at first view. They might see ad multiples time which will influence and persuade them to try your product.\r\n<h2>Negative impact of television on marketing;</h2>\r\nJust like every other thing TV ads also have some dark corners. Few are;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>TV ads cost pretty much because channels do only charge for advertising but they also case their popularity. Cost also depends on ad duration, when are you broadcasting it and which areas are you broadcasting it in.</li>\r\n	<li>You must pay product experts and other team experts too to prepare your ad.</li>\r\n	<li>If you need to change anything you will have to reshoot the complete ad which will cost double.</li>\r\n	<li>Showing it once or twice to customers is not enough. The ad must be displayed at least 6 or 7 times to the consumer to grab its attention.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTV marketing is suitable for every type of business of any range and size. It can catch attention of customers for them from anywhere.','Impact of television on marketing','','inherit','open','open','','246-revision-v1','','','2015-04-12 15:36:43','2015-04-12 19:36:43','',246,'http://adomattic.com/246-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(263,2,'2015-04-16 23:11:51','2015-04-17 03:11:51','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMobile advertising that lies under mobile marketing is considered as one of the best ad practices. The reason is that it makes advertisers reach their customers on the go. Term “mobile ad” raises a thought in your mind that it might be a banner kind of ad or ads in search results. But the new advancements have made it go further than this. Mobile ads subsist in different number of formats now such as banners; short message service (SMS), short videos, vibration based sound ads and other responsive and interactive display ads. Both marketers and app publishers need to run their own ads to promote their apps and other products. Mobile advertising is suitable for every kind of business and app to be promoted.\r\n<h2>What to know before advertising on mobile?</h2>\r\nBefore you run ad on mobile you should consider the following points;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What are the types of mobile ads that advertisers can make use of</li>\r\n	<li>What are different mobile devices that you will be running your ad on like smartphone, blackberry, iPhones and other devices that can make calls?</li>\r\n	<li>How can user click on the ad, what are the easiest and preferred ways?</li>\r\n	<li>Understand conversion rates.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Where mobile ads can appear and their types</h2>\r\n<table style=\"height: 554px; margin: 5px;\" border=\"2\" width=\"607\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<