xperts. This can be considered as one of the most appealing advantage for marketers.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Persuade your customers</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen your ad is broadcasted and customers see it, they never place orders at first view. They might see the ad multiples time which will influence and persuade them to try your product.\r\n<h2>Negative impact of television on marketing;</h2>\r\nJust like every other thing TV ads also have some dark corners. Few are;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>TV ads cost pretty much because channels do only charge for advertising, but they also cash their popularity. Cost also depends on ad duration, when are you broadcasting it and which areas are you broadcasting it in.</li>\r\n	<li>You must pay product experts and other team experts too to prepare your ad.</li>\r\n	<li>If you need to change anything you will have to reshoot the complete ad which will cost double.</li>\r\n	<li>Showing it once or twice to customers is not enough. The ad must be displayed at least 6 or 7 times to the consumer to grab its attention.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTV marketing is suitable for every type of business of any range and size. It can catch the attention of customers for them from anywhere.','Impact of television on marketing','','inherit','open','open','','246-revision-v1','','','2015-04-24 06:05:15','2015-04-24 10:05:15','',246,'http://adomattic.com/246-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(418,2,'2015-04-24 06:06:50','2015-04-24 10:06:50','','images (7)','','inherit','open','open','','images-7','','','2015-04-24 06:06:50','2015-04-24 10:06:50','',246,'http://adomattic.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/images-7.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(419,2,'2015-04-24 06:07:55','2015-04-24 10:07:55','Television has been leaving its impacts on advertising since long ago. With encroachments in technology and user demands, number of channels is also increased. Today’s purchaser is multi-channel bargain hunter. They cross-check the information they get from 