ads are;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Great possibility of customer’s visit to the content and surety of user’s response.</li>\r\n	<li>Consumers consider them content and view them for same number of seconds.</li>\r\n	<li>Effective to obtain branding goals.</li>\r\n	<li>The increase purchase rate 18% higher than banner ads.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe native content that is about viewer, reader and listener is one considered best. Native ads are supposed to enhance the quality of content by providing relevant ads to guide the reader.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPhoto Credit : https://www.flickr.com/photos/r00s/','What Is Native Advertisement?','','inherit','open','open','','90-revision-v1','','','2015-04-24 07:00:29','2015-04-24 11:00:29','',90,'http://adomattic.com/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (436,2,'2015-04-24 10:13:41','2015-04-24 14:13:41','Contextual advertisements take place using specific keywords from the websites or from the search terms used by consumers. The websites that are targeted to some specific area contain keywords which are used by contextual advertisement scripts to produce and display relevant advertisements to the visitors. Such as website dedicated to food recopies will contain words relevant to foods hence script will fetch the advertisements of best food restaurants or newly written books on continental foods. Contextual advertisements can be displayed as ads on website with other web content or as pop-ups. Search engines display contextual advertisements by showing them in search results to the searcher.\n\n<img src=\"http://media.rusbase.com/blogs/context-advertising.jpg\" alt=\"contextual advertisement \" />\n\n<i>image by logical operations at their website {link to <a title=\"logical operations\" href=\"http://info.logicaloperations.com/google-adwords-analytics-training/\" target=\"_blank\">http://info.logicaloperations.com/google-adwords-analytics-training/</a>} </i>\n\n<b>Latest trends in contextual advertisement</b>\n\n<b>            </b>Advanced trends, enhanced scripts and faster algorithms are used to display relevant advertisements on a web page. Here we are mentioning some latest trends and facts about contextual advertisement.\n<ul>\n	<li>Developers and advertisers are introducing new trends to present customized information and message to their audience. Several ways are devised to fetch more information about the consumers.</li>\n	<li>Showing relevant advertisements on web-pages is the core motive of contextual advertisement. Programmers are using latest technologies called Mediabot and Googlebot to fetch related advertisements only.</li>\n	<li>Gaming is also used as a mean to advertise but in the beginning experience did not produce positive results. Companies embedded advertisements at the time game was loading but players showed great annoyance. Advertisers are now searching for better ways. Many games are now inserting advertisements at different scenes of games without affecting player’s game experience.</li>\n	<li>Video-on-video or text on video at the time of loading is also applied. ScanScout and Adsense is a latest technology that scans the content of video and offer only relevant advertisements.</li>\n	<li>Publishers and advertisers now prefer collaborative working to earn more profit. Both Google and Yahoo have introduced their own ways of pricing at advertisements. Google’s smart pricing scheme allows setting prices dynamically while yahoo lets to set one price for each company rather than setting dynamic costs for products.</li>\n	<li>The trend that will be more common in near future is billboard contextual advertising. This advertising comprises using cameras with billboards and recording the expressions, time duration person spent on reading advertisements, and their responses. Advertisers can use this direct information for further functions.</li>\n</ul>\n<b> Controversies</b>\n\nContextual advertisements called to controversies when unfair means were used to display them on sites without paying them. Third party software is installed on visitor’s computer. This software interacts with the browser and converts keywords on the websites into hyperlinks to the advertisements without paying the website. This technique is known as Third part hyperlinking. There are many such techniques used to illegally advertise on the websites without their permission.\n\nDifferent formats of Contextual advertisement not just compute users preferences but their behaviors as well. Developers and advertisers are working to enhance the ways of displaying advertisements to the relevant users. Contextual advertisement is now becoming one of the major sources of earning for websites.\n\nPhoto Credit: https://www.flickr.com/photos/proimos/','What Is Contex