tes. It defines how customers will access you through your ads from different websites such as clicks, double clicks etc. Applying conversion rates doesn’t cost much and can drive heavy traffic to your website.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Retention plan </strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Retention strategy is about making a strong hold on your customers. The strategy defines how to engage more with your customers. Within this strategy you need to have a wealth of data about customers and you must analyze them to have deep insights for understanding their interest patterns. These analytics will also help you understand what ways are preferred more by your customers for interaction and purchases.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Analytics and management strategy</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">            Web analytics and management is about collecting, measuring, evaluating and reporting online data to optimize website usage. In this strategy you will cover-up what analytics you need from customer’s data and how you will actually be analyzing the data. Furthermore how are you going manage all the analyzed data besides with other information?</span>','Simple Digital Marketing Strategies','','inherit','open','open','','474-revision-v1','','','2015-05-01 12:21:25','2015-05-01 16:21:25','',474,'http://adomattic.com/474-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(480,2,'2015-05-02 04:44:41','2015-05-02 08:44:41','<span style=\"color: #000000;\">In our last article we discussed <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http://adomattic.com/simple-digital-marketing-strategies/\">simple digital marketing strategies</a>. There we gave major idea of “proposition strategy” but here we are going to see in depth what a value proposition is and how you can develop a well-organized value proposition for your on