ke <em>\"What does this website have for me?”</em></span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Why do we need an online proposition strategy</strong>?</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To hook new visitors with your website.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To distinguish your website from that of competitors.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Draws a clear line about the purpose of website.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Can increase word-of-mouth advertising in case is clear and based on facts.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>What to define in proposition strategy?</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">You are supposed to describe following things about your business in proposition strategy.</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">We have got good team and experts.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">We provide best quality.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">We are always near and on time whenever you need us.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">We provide best and affordable prices.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Proposition value equation</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">According to findings here is the value proposition equation.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Perceived value= benefits-cost (Risk)</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Be careful when you design proposition strategy</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Remember! Only add facts to your proposition strategy. Never write what you will be but write what you are. Never promise what you cannot fulfill in future. Include what are the desires of your targeted market and how can you fulfill it by using you’re your abilities. It should be realistic and must have deep insight of your targeted audience. Nothing can catch your customers more than proving what you can do for them. Don’t boast but prove.</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <img src=\"http://cdn2.hubspot.net/hub/153059/file-31115023-png/images/screen_shot_2013-04-25_at_11.01.34_am.png\" alt=\"proposition strategy\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Image by ops rules at their website {Link to <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http://www.opsrules.com/supply-chain-optimization-blog/bid/287149/To-refresh-your-supply-chain-strategy-start-with-the-customer\">http://www.opsrules.com/supply-chain-optimization-blog/bid/287149/To-refresh-your-supply-chain-strategy-start-with-the-customer</a>}</span>','Proposition strategy — what to keep in view','','publish','open','open','','proposition-strategy-keep-view','','\nhttp://adomattic.com/simple-digital-marketing-strategies/','2015-05-02 09:59:50','2015-05-02 13:59:50','',0,'http://adomattic.com/?p=480',0,'post','',0),(481,2,'2015-05-02 04:44:41','2015-05-02 08:44:41','In our last article we discussed <a href=\"http://adomattic.com/simple-digital-marketing-strategies/\">simple digital marketing strategies</a>. There we gave major idea of “proposition strategy” but here we are going to see in depth what a value proposition is and how you can develop a well-organized value proposition for your online business.\r\n\r\nHow is product unique? Why buyers should buy from you? What is different about you that other competitors are failed to excel? These questions make base of your business. You will not be able to set a successful business strategy if you are failed to answer these questions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Online proposition strategy and value</strong>\r\n\r\nHave you ever visited a website and then thought ‘why am I on this website?’, ‘will it help me’, ‘will I get what I need’, and then you just left.\r\n\r\nA concise online value proposition is a critical method to clasp new visitors into your website and brand in those central seconds that a visitor is making a decision to click-on or leave out your website. It also heartens continued practice and support about your website, so it\'s very important to an efficient web strategy and policy.\r\n\r\nAn online proposition strategy is directly tied to your brand positioning which answers problems such as: who we are and what we present, what are our targeted markets, what is unique about us? But your proposition details enlarges this the difference is that it recognizes the causes why users will click on, return, signup or purchase from your website and preferably feel provoked enough to share their experience.\r\n\r\nIt should define what benefits your buyer will get from your website, its content, your web services or functionalities and how is it all related to your services or product. It\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt should not just be your brand guarantee or a more broadly client value proposition stuck online, as that fails to spot the point that someone is on your website now and asking themselves questions like <em>\"What does this website have for me?”</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Why do we need an online proposition strategy</strong>?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To hook new visitors with your website.</li>\r\n	<li>To distinguish your website from that of competitors.</li>\r\n	<li>Draws a clear line about the purpose of website.</li>\r\n	<li>Can increase word-of-mouth advertising in case is clear and based on facts.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>What to define in proposition strategy?</strong>\r\n\r\nYou are supposed to describe following things about your business in proposition strategy.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We have got good team and experts.</li>\r\n	<li>We provide best quality.</li>\r\n	<li>We are always near and on time whenever you need us.</li>\r\n	<li>We provide best and affordable prices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Proposition value equation</strong>\r\n\r\nAccording to findings here is the value proposition equation.\r\n\r\nPerceived value= benefits-cost (Risk)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Be careful when you design proposition strategy</strong>\r\n\r\nRemember! Only add facts to your proposition strategy. Never write what you will be but write what you are. Never promise what you cannot fulfill in future. Include what are the desires of your targeted market and how can you fulfill it by using you’re your abilities. It should be realistic and must have deep insight of your targeted audience. Nothing can catch your customers more than proving what you can do for them. Don’t boast but prove.','Designing Proposition strategy—what to keep in view','','inherit','open','open','','480-revision-v1','','','2015-05-02 04:44:41','2015-05-02 08:44:41','',480,'http://adomattic.com/480-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(482,2,'2015-05-02 09:57:11','2015-05-02 13:57:11','<span style=\"color: #000000;\">In our last article we discussed <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http://adomattic.com/simple-digital-marketing-strategies/\">simple digital marketing strategies</a>. There we gave major idea of “proposition strategy” but here we are going to see in depth what a value proposition is and how you can develop a well-organized value proposition for your online business.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">How is product unique? Why buyers should buy from you? What is different about you that other competitors are failed to excel? These questions make base of your business. You will not be able to set a successful business strategy if you are failed to answer these questions.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Online proposition strategy and value</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Have you ever visited a website and then thought ‘why am I on this website?’, ‘will it help me’, ‘will I get