s with Hadoop. It’s developed on the top of Hbase which is a database layer built over Hadoop. Using WibiData users can collect user information and can analyse them in more effective manner. It also enables  real-time responses to users interests and behaviors for instance, displaying data according to previous search patters, showing personalized content and decisions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>PLATFORA</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>            </strong>Hadoop is a low level implemenmtation of MapReduce that is its major weakness and drawback. This makes it require to be operated by professionals only. Their techniques such as testing, processing and preparing take large amount of time. Which doesn’t allow users to enjoy their experiences. But PLATFORA platform converts user’s queries into Hadoop queries and tasks. That’s the technique it uses to create abstraction layer that can be used by anyone to simplify and structure datasets saved in Hadoop.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Big Data in the cloud</strong>\r\n\r\nResearch and studies have shown that a large number of big data techniques are linked with cloud. Already hosted Hadoop clusters are being sold by large number of vendors. These Hadoop clusters are designed according to user’s requirements. Previous techniques mentioned in the articles either have cloud versions built into them or are completely cloud based. Cloud computing have enabled companies to have more value of their large data than ever before.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Latest Big Data Technologies','','inherit','open','open','','611-revision-v1','','','2015-05-11 16:34:19','2015-05-11 20:34:19','',611,'http://adomattic.com/611-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(613,2,'2015-05-11 16:36:18','2015-05-11 20:36:18','','cyanocitta_cristata-1280x800','','inherit','open','open','','cyanocitta_cristata-1280x800','','','2015-05-11 16:36:18','2015-05-11 20:36:18','',611,'http://adomattic.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/cyanocitta_cristata-1280