o target audience with mobile marketing. The research has placed mobile marketing as among the best ways for communication, reaching out people and to target audience with mobile marketing. Almost every company today is trying to nail out more effective and easy ways to catch their targeted audience. They are trying to surpass one another in this race . Clearly recognizing and targeting the intended users is the biggest challenge and milestone for marketers. Once you are done with grabbing targeted users then you can get further information from them. This information can be much valuable in order to recognize customer’s interests. You can further ask users for more conversions and purchases. Every marketer needs to set-up a strategy for best mobile marketing. Here are some tactics that can work amazingly.\r\n<h3>Offer a user friendly mobile experience</h3>\r\nA friendly and easy mobile experience is so much important that its absence can even result in failure of best planned Mobile Relationship Marketing (MRM) strategy. If your company have a website then it must be mobile friendly and responsive. All users regardless of the devices, operating systems and mobile phone browsers they use, must have almost similar experience. As web technology is going through so many changes and every day new techniques are emerging. So need to keep your website up-to-date. It can cost you enough so be ready for that.\r\n<h3>Location based Discounts</h3>\r\nIn current times, there are several ways to hyper-target your targeted users with the help of social media platforms that are already used by mobile users. You can use Facebook, Yahoo, Google+ and other similar ways to inform your local customers about deals. Based on locations you can offer exciting discounts and prizes to your audience. This will increase their interest in you.\r\n<h3>Simplify the Sharing Process</h3>\r\nDon’t make your mobile marketing campaign a one-way street. Make sharing your content feasible for your current users. Allow them to share it with their contacts. Offer exciting prizes, discounts and services to referrers. Provide options for sharing your ads on social media platforms too. This can help you to have an insight of what mobile marketing avenues are best for you and how you can increase your conversion rates and ROI.\r\n<h3>Mobile video marketing</h3>\r\nPeople today are heavily influenced by images and videos. A short clip based on product information, service details or simply to raise awareness can catch user’s attention. YouTube is the top platform for uploading and sharing videos plus it also allows sharing links in videos. If worked handled bit professionally, videos can spread enough awareness in your users about what you offer.\r\n<h3>Boost Customer maintenance with SMS &amp; Email</h3>\r\nIn comparison to other ways Email and mobile SMSs are noticed as best user engaging methods. Through them you can send latest news and information of new deals to your consumers.\r\n<h3>Final Word</h3>\r\nIn today’s world of marketing attention is money. You need to refine your methods according to preferences of your users and it must be your top priority.\r\n<img class=\" aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.mmoneyonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/5-Mobile-Marketing-Trends1.jpg\" width=\"954px\" height=\"863px\" />\r\nImage at <a href=\"http://www.mmoneyonline.com/hit-your-target-with-a-mobile-marketing-agency/\">http://www.mmoneyonline.com/hit-your-target-with-a-mobile-marketing-agency/</a>','Hold target audience with mobile marketing','','publish','open','open','','hold-target-audience-with-mobile-marketing','','','2015-05-15 12:37:22','2015-05-15 16:37:22','',0,'http://adomattic.com/?p=634',0,'post','',0),(635,2,'2015-05-15 12:14:56','2015-05-15 16:14:56','With the advent of wireless technology for mobile phones every company can be seen trying to figure out best ways to target audience with mobile marketing. The research has placed mobile marketing as among the 