y difficult to find out valuable results from a mass data. The data can be abput anything such has user, weather, devices, population and a lot more. This issue provokes a though of planning for something better and faster. Something that would be more meaningful and easy to evaluate. The answer that emerged is “Fast Data”. Speed holds immense value in this era of data-driven, highly-connected and information intensive technology.\r\nWhat do you think of getting the data instantly when you need it? experts say, biggest issue of data can only be resolved if we get required data as quickly as we get any new information. As slow data is one of the biggest problems.\r\n<h3>Is big data as useful as fast data?</h3>\r\nProfessional analysts claim that looking into myth of big data deeply is not necessary. Big data is a buzzword for which we need to have several things to workout with. Big data is so complicated that alone and without using higher technologies no work can be done effectively. In such cases what is more preferable is looking into repeatable pattern. Of course studying whole data is not very easy. So to cut the task small datasets, repeated patterns and model of data is analyzed. They are analysed in short time with faster timelines. Experts prefer Fast data a lot more than big data.\r\nNow what actually fast data is? Here is a major definition\r\n“The Fast Data platform combines three major assets: your data, people, and technology, providing real-time awareness to take instant action. Your competition might have the same data. But with the ability to make informed decisions—and quickly taking action while the outcome is still in play—you can change what happens next…while your competition is still crunching their numbers. ”\r\nBy <a href=\"http://www.tibco.com/fastdata\">http://www.tibco.com/fastdata</a>\r\nFast data gives real time decision making capability and quantitative feedback to company that would effectively enhance company’s bottom-line.\r\n\r\n<strong>Actions included in fast data can be;</strong>\r\n• Generating and processing quick reports on different conversion types for paid ads, paid search, call-only and other similar ones.\r\n• Fast data makes it easy to measure how many clicks or number of actions is required by sales representative to create an active sales cycle for its buyers.\r\n• Specifies what conversion, ads messaging, interaction ways are better to enhance velocity of sales cycle.\r\n• Helps more in checking what the search patterns of users are.\r\n\r\nBig data remained as a hot topic of research, development and discussion for so long but now it’s getting replaced with a new and more effective term “fast data”. A lot of research and work is going on over how to migrate from big to fast data for better future. This is important to impact our businesses for better and to take better decisions. In this age of propinquity actionable data is a blood to organizations for providing better services to consumers.\r\n<img src=\"http://www.viewpoint.fr/uploads/media/product/0001/01/images%20/vp%20FRM%20tableau%201.1.jpg\" alt=\"fast data\" />\r\nImage at<a href=\"http://www.viewpoint.fr/en/p/software/fastdata-monitor\"> http://www.viewpoint.fr/en/p/software/fastdata-monitor</a>','why Fast Data is getting more popularity than Big Data','','publish','open','open','','why-fast-data-is-getting-more-popularity-than-big-data','','','2015-05-24 16:17:14','2015-05-24 20:17:14','',0,'http://adomattic.com/?p=708',0,'post','',0),(709,2,'2015-05-24 16:05:33','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-05-24 16:05:33','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://adomattic.com/?p=709',0,'post','',0),(710,2,'2015-05-24 16:08:51','2015-05-24 20:08:51','Big data can give a big challenge in terms of analysis, evaluation and figuring out meaningful results. It’s really difficult to find out valuable results from a mass data. The data can be abput anything such has user, weather, device